  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/0c341874d48a28544c018d973791cc49.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=74 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Returning from an expedition to South America, you assume the role of an archaeologist who discovered an ancient sacred site of a long-forgotten civilization. Eager to share your findings with your family, you look forward to recounting your journey and meticulously documenting everything in your study. <br><br>Unbeknownst to you, however, you've brought something else back, and your family is mysteriously absent upon your return…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/62ea2e7bd76669d3c6663664bf9c48c8.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>The whole world at your finger tips! Interact with (almost) any object imaginable in this immersive puzzle experience and use your investigative skills to solve puzzles and riddles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/b4fca3d3f638c323d0a8383015e43195.poster.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=205 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/b4fca3d3f638c323d0a8383015e43195.webm?t=1745395407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/c4c5ba37782cf595affdaeb6d2645660.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>Traverse the ever changing hallway, challenge ancient gods, and solve their puzzles and riddles. Collect necessary items to progress and find your way out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/8f6297461a3c05d5ade0b0787d0d13c5.poster.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=205 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/8f6297461a3c05d5ade0b0787d0d13c5.webm?t=1745395407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/dacd04292f498ac74dcb11b44db86040.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>Unravel what happened to you and your family upon your return. Learn more about the discoveries that you've made and try to uncover all the mysteries surrounding them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/7cf5f640080f91f7ef0227d59e25fd4b.poster.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=205 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/7cf5f640080f91f7ef0227d59e25fd4b.webm?t=1745395407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Returning from an expedition to South America, you assume the role of an archaeologist who discovered an ancient sacred site of a long-forgotten civilization. Eager to share your findings with your family, you look forward to recounting your journey and meticulously documenting everything in your study. <br><br>Unbeknownst to you, however, you've brought something else back, and your family is mysteriously absent upon your return…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/62ea2e7bd76669d3c6663664bf9c48c8.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>The whole world at your finger tips! Interact with (almost) any object imaginable in this immersive puzzle experience and use your investigative skills to solve puzzles and riddles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/b4fca3d3f638c323d0a8383015e43195.poster.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=205 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/b4fca3d3f638c323d0a8383015e43195.webm?t=1745395407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/c4c5ba37782cf595affdaeb6d2645660.avif?t=1745395407\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>Traverse the ever changing hallway, challenge ancient gods, and solve their puzzles and riddles. Collect necessary items to progress and find your way out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541740/extras/8f6297461a3c05d5ade0b0787d0d13c5.poster.avi